      "text": "{\"output\":{\"content\":\"Tools (March 2026) for monitoring AI answer‑engine citations (ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews/AI, Perplexity)\\n\\n1. Dedicated AI citation / visibility trackers  \\n- **OtterlyAI** – Tracks brand mentions and website citations across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI Overviews, Gemini, Copilot; shows “Share of AI Voice” and which queries you win/lose. [[1, 2]]\\n- **Peec AI** – Prompt‑level rank tracker for ChatGPT that also monitors visibility across Perplexity, Google AI Overviews, Copilot, Gemini. Focus on structured reporting, competitor comparisons, share of voice, and citation sources. [[3, 4, 5]]\\n- **Siftly** – GEO‑focused platform measuring mentions + source citations across ChatGPT, Google AI Overviews, Gemini, Perplexity; emphasizes competitive share of voice and citation positioning. [[6]]\\n- **AIclicks / LLMclicks** – Tracks prompt‑level visibility and citations in ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI Overviews, Gemini, Claude, etc.; dashboards for mentions, rankings, and citation sources. [[7, 4]]\\n- **Rankability (Rankability Reporter / AI Analyzer)** – GEO + AI search visibility suite that identifies where your brand is cited (or not) across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI Overviews, plus content‑gap fixing workflows. [[8, 5]]\\n- **Athena** – GEO platform combining prompt tracking, brand monitoring, competitive benchmarks, and citation / content‑gap detection across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI Overviews/Mode, Gemini, Claude, Copilot, Grok. [[5]]\\n- **Scrunch AI, Gauge, Rankscale, Akii, Profound, Promptmonitor** – Additional monitoring tools called out in 2026 comparison roundups; focus areas include detailed prompt analysis, daily AI‑answer monitoring, sentiment, and page‑level citation tracking across major answer engines. [[2, 9, 10, 11]] \\n\\n2. Research / benchmarking data sources (to understand platform behavior)  \\n- **Profound “AI Platform Citation Patterns”**
